title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\Model\ExportFormat
name: ExportFormat
description:
Represents export format supported by the Model.

All formats export to Google Cloud Storage.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.Model.ExportFormat

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.id
params.description: Output only. The ID of the export format. The possible format IDs are: tflite Used for Android mobile devices. edgetpu-tflite Used for Edge TPU devices. tf-saved-model A tensorflow model in SavedModel format. tf-js A TensorFlow.js model that can be used in the browser and in Node.js using JavaScript. core-ml Used for iOS mobile devices. custom-trained A Model that was uploaded or trained by custom code.

params.name: data.exportable_contents
params.description: Output only. The content of this Model that may be exported.
